1
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:21,800
Sir,

2
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:22,760
excuse me.

3
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:24,960
We have a long-term event going on.

4
00:00:25,120 --> 00:00:26,960
Just take a photo with your meal,

5
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:29,680
put it on the wish wall over there,

6
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:31,480
write down your wish on a card,

7
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,240
and you'll get a free dessert.

8
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:34,600
No, thanks.

9
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,760
Come on, join us.

10
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,200
This week's limited time offer, only two days left!

11
00:00:45,360 --> 00:00:45,920
Sorry.

12
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:46,920
Well,

13
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:48,200
this one's for you.

14
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:23,640
She...

15
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,080
Didn't write a wish?

16
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,880
I ate a cookie here today.

17
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,880
It's not as good as the one I baked for you.

18
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:04,760
But,

19
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,240
I hope you find

20
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,520
something even better somewhere else.

21
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:10,720
F

22
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,640
It's raining.

23
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,480
I don't have an umbrella.

24
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,000
Don't get wet.

25
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:18,880
F

26
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,160
My thesis was praised by my supervisor.

27
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:23,960
If you were here,

28
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,040
you would probably sneer at me.

29
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:27,680
But

30
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,680
I still want to tell you.

31
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,640
I hope you also have

32
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,160
something small to be happy about.

33
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:34,840
F.

34
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,240
The New Year is coming.

35
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,640
Another year.

36
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,080
I hope you are safe and healthy.

37
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,680
Live well in some corner.

38
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,480
Happy New Year.

39
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,560
F.

40
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,600
Today is my birthday.

41
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,520
[But]

42
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,160
[the earrings you gave me]

43
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,120
[are long gone.]

44
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,840
[F]

45
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,120
Fu,

46
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,640
you look much better lately.

47
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,280
And you haven't had a relapse.

48
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,680
The doctor told me

49
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,200
there's a good chance you can fully recover.

50
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,960
You'll be fine.

51
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,200
Look at me,

52
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,760
I'm not in a position to talk about this.

53
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,520
How have you been through these two years?

54
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,320
Others may not know,

55
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,480
but I do.

56
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,760
You can stand here now,

57
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,880
and you can control yourself. That's already good.

58
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:50,240
Am I too cowardly?

59
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,800
I don't have the courage to face her at all.

60
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,240
Brother Fu,

61
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:55,880
just think of it

62
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,080
to live up to the words Yan wrote.

63
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,520
At least,

64
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,120
don't let her talk to the wall anymore.

65
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,600
Tian Yan.

66
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:39,920
I'm busy.

67
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,560
Last time...

68
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,240
Sorry.

69
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,800
There are some special circumstances.

70
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,360
You don't have to explain to me.

71
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,680
Mr. Fu.

72
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,640
Long time no see.

73
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,760
I have a lot to tell you.

74
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,920
How about having dinner together?

75
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,480
My treat.

76
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,400
Sorry, I have a class.

77
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,800
I'll wait for you.

78
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,720
You're off class.

79
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,960
Pang Jingfu, stop following me.

80
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,040
You can pretend I don't exist.

81
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,360
Or

82
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,680
just pretend there's an extra shadow.

83
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,120
The once lofty Mr. Fu

84
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,280
now

85
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,920
you're my shadow.

86
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,920
How the tables have turned.

87
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:56,520
Yes.

88
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:59,080
I can be whatever you want me to be.

89
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,080
A follower,

90
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:02,880
a bodyguard,

91
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,040
or a servant at your command.

92
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,560
A follower,

93
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,200
a maid,

94
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,160
whatever you need me to be,

95
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:13,960
as you wish,

96
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,680
as long as you're happy.

97
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,560
That's satisfying.

98
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,000
Tian Yan.

99
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,840
Pang Jingfu,

100
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,320
I don't want to argue with you anymore.

101
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,800
I'll tell you calmly now,

102
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,720
in the past,

103
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,000
I approached you with a purpose,

104
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,240
but now,

105
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,000
I've thought it over,

106
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,360
we come from two different worlds.

107
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,840
A broken mirror can be mended,

108
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,120
but ours was shattered from the start.

109
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,760
Tian Yan,

110
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,760
I just want a chance,

111
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,800
a chance to pick up the pieces.

112
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,360
Even a glance would be enough.

113
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,720
Tian Yan,

114
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,640
what must I do

115
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,080
to earn this chance from you?

116
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,080
An opportunity?

117
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,800
Unless you kneel down

118
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,480
and beg me.

119
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,680
Tian Yan,

120
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,840
what else do you want me to do?

121
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,480
Tell me.

122
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,640
I beg you.

123
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,960
Stop doing these useless things.

124
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,200
I don't want to be involved with anyone

125
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,880
whose hands are stained with blood.

126
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:43,760
I didn't kill him.

127
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,640
I didn't kill Li Hen.

128
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,200
I swear.

129
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,360
Then where is he now?

130
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:50,440
I don't know.

131
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:53,160
You forced me to hold the gun.

132
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,960
I watched him shoot himself to save me.

133
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,120
He died in front of me.

134
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,640
And you're trying to tell me

135
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:00,040
that

136
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:00,760
of this.

137
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:01,800
I can explain.

138
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,280
I already sent Yan Hong...

139
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:04,000
Stop!

140
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,280
I won't believe a word you say.

141
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,640
Just let me go.

142
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,600
Please.

143
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,760
The cases I just showed you

144
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:56,000
should be very useful

145
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:58,480
for your research this semester.

146
00:08:58,800 --> 00:08:59,880
Guys, come here.

147
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,600
How are you feeling today?

148
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,440
Are you still in pain?

149
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:07,120
Help!

150
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,600
What's that noise?

151
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:15,080
Probably just the wind.

152
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,560
Wind?

153
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:37,960
Excuse me,

154
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,080
what can I help you with?

155
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:41,400
This is a restricted area.

156
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,440
I thought I heard

157
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,560
something strange inside.

158
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:46,280
Listen.

159
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,280
This is Professor Bovis's private research lab.

160
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:52,120
It involves top-secret medical research projects.

161
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:55,360
No one is allowed to enter or approach without authorization.

162
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,600
Please leave.

163
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,000
Please return to your team.

164
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,040
Immediately.

165
00:09:59,160 --> 00:09:59,880
Okay?

166
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:01,680
Go back.

167
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,480
No.

168
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:24,880
There must be something wrong.

169
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:08,760
Professor,

170
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,240
researchers need to see you.

171
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,440
It's urgent.

172
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,080
Ah.

173
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,360
I'm sorry. Wrong way.

174
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,760
Live well with me from now on.

175
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:38,760
Watch out.

176
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:39,400
Thank you.

177
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:47,320
Master.
